file: /cmds/mortal/acronyms.c
keywords: mortal, miscellaneous
aliases: acrophobia, acronyms
short: The Acronyms Game
header: Topic: The Acronyms Game

  SYNTAX:  acronyms

Acronyms is a mud-based version of Acrophobia(TM), a hybrid of
the original IRC game and the Berkeley Systems web game.  Typing
this command will create an Acronyms Aura in your inventory which
will allow you to play Acronyms.  Once you have the Acronyms Aura,
type 'acro' for further information.


