file: /cmds/mortal/cbrief.c
keywords: mortal, miscellaneous, combat, attack
aliases: 
short: Combat Briefer
header: Topic: Combat Brief

  SYNTAX:  cbrief <args>

     Combat Briefing
 Commands:
  cbrief on [full] - Brief the attacks you see, full = show nothing.
  cbrief on [mo]   - 'Misses Only', don't show misses, show normal attacks.
  cbrief off       - Return to normal attack messages.
  cbrief monster   - Turn a critter's attacks brief (toggle).
                     Note: This has little to no utility since briefing
                           is per person now, but it might be useful on
                           a guild follower or something.

