file: /cmds/mortal/converse.c
keywords: mortal, communication, tell, say, ask
aliases: 
short: Start a conversation without having to type say/tell
header: Topic: converse

  SYNTAX:  converse [line]

This command puts your character into a state where everything you
type in thereafter will be 'said' by your character.  This allows you
to more easily have long conversations with people and to also cut and
paste multi-line pieces of text.  To exit the converse mode, enter **
on a single line by itself.
You can alternatively specify a chat line as an argument to
converse, and you'll converse on that line.
e.g. converse chat
     converse tell sally
    etc...


