file: /cmds/mortal/dispose.c
keywords: mortal, basic, inv, i, mi, eq
aliases: 
short:  Dispose of an item
header: Topic: Dispose

  SYNTAX:  dispose <item>
      OR:  dispose <all>

Disposing of an item destroys the item from existence,
freeing up space in your inventory and in the game's memory.

  dispose <item>: disposes an item in your inventory.
  dispose <all>:  disposes of all unkept items in your inventory.

Example

     ex: dispose sword

This will dispose of (destroy) your sword.


