aliases:
short: The Events Tool
header: Topic:  Events Tool

  SYNTAX:  events <string>

The 'events' command will allow you to see what events are going on
right now, as well as upcoming and past events.  You can talk on it too, but
don't abuse it - it's really only meant for discussion around events.
You can 'events list' to get a listing of scheduled, ongoing, and past events
You can 'events info <name>' to get detailed information about a scheduled
or ongoing event.  You cannot get information for past events.
You can 'events off' or 'events on' to turn if off and then on again.

