--------------------
file: /cmds/mortal/get.c
keywords: mortal, take, basic, drop, keep, unkeep
aliases: 
short: Get an object in the room
header: Topic Get

  SYNTAX:  get <object> OR get all

The 'get' and 'take' commands allow the player to pick up items
from the ground, provided they are able to take on that much more
weight in their inventories.  Not all objects are able to be taken,
of course, for various reasons.

This command will also accept 'all' as an argument, and this will
cause you to attempt to pick up everything on the ground in front
of you.  Of course, weight is one of the considerations that would
prevent you from being able to take something.


