as well and responds to all the regular flags.

--------------------
file: /cmds/mortal/give.c
keywords: mortal, basic, keep, unkeep
aliases: 
short: Give an object to someone/thing
header: Command: Give

  SYNTAX:  give <object> to <monster or person>
     OR:  give all to <monster or person>

The 'give' command allows a player to give one object to a monster
or another player, provided the object is in fact droppable.  Some
objects(for instance, guild objects) are coded so that they cannot
be given away to others, for various reasons.

This command may also take 'all' as a first argument, which will
cause you to attempt to give all unkept items to the monster or
player in question.


