file: /cmds/mortal/glimpse.c
keywords: glimpse
aliases: 
short: Seeing into the next room
header: Command: glimpse

   Syntax:   glimpse <exit>

The glimpse command allows you to skillfully gain a quick peek into an
adjacent room.  You must have a high skill in Perception to be able to
use this ability, and the exertion to do so requires that you rest a
length of time before you can try again.  The length of the rest can be
reduced by having at least rudimentary skill in Evasion and Survival.

   Example

glimpse east
glimpse down

