--------------------
file: /cmds/mortal/lottery.c
keywords: miscellaneous
aliases: 
short:  Getting Gear on the Cheap
header: Topic: lottery

  SYNTAX:  lottery [cmd]

Command options:
 show    - Shows what's in the lottery and how long until awarded
 cost    - How much is it to buy a ticket?
 buy     - Buy a lottery ticket!
 history - Check the lottery history.
 ignore  - Ignore lotteries for remainder of boot. (toggles)
 collect - You won, but were offline, get it.
 chat    - Talk on the lottery line (or 'lotchat').
 offer   - Put an item on for the lottery!


The lottery system is YOUR CHANCE to snag an epic level item offered
by a titled wizard!  Rather than see how high an auction bid can get,
this lottery is open to anyone with at least 100 coins.
Buy a lottery ticket before the lottery ends, and if your name is
drawn, you instantly get the item! (If you are offline, see above.)

You can buy more than one lottery ticket, however, each one past the
first costs 10x as much as the prior. (up to 7 tickets)
(Subsequent purchases require confirmation.)


