file: /cmds/mortal/remindme.c
keywords:
aliases:
short: 3K Reminder System
header: 3K Reminder System

SYNTAX:  remindme         (Summon a reminder tool)
         remind on        (Activate TMC Reminder tool)
         remind off       (Deactivate TMC Reminder tool)
         remind tmc       (Acknowledge TMC reminder, you will not be
                           reminded for 24 hours.)
         remind destroy   (Destroy your reminder tool)

Once you have triggered a reminder, you will be reminded every 30 minutes
until you ackowledge that reminder.  Turning your reminder off and back
on will immediately start reminding you.

