header: Command: Showaddr
::::::::::::::::::::::
    Topic: showaddr
::::::::::::::::::::::

  Syntax:  showaddr

When you first logged on to 3-kingdoms you were required to give a
working email address. You were also asked if you want this address
to be visible to all the other players. At the time, you choose what
you saw fit and began to play the game. Years later, you changed your
mind and by the use of 'showaddr' you can make your email address
visible and invisible when someone fingers you.
Pretty nifty, don't you think?


