--------------------
file: /cmds/mortal/smuggle.c
keywords: mortal, carry
aliases:
short: Smuggling items in your inventory
header: Command: smuggle
Assuming you are skilled in this ability, smuggle allows you to stash items
in a special pocket.  This pocket is so special that not only will others be
unable to see you carrying the items, but the items smuggled will not count
against your carrying encumberance.

SYNTAX: smuggle               - lists any currently smuggled items
        smuggle [item]        - smuggles [item] into your pocket
        smuggle remove [item] - removes [item] from your pocket
        smuggle remove all    - removes all smuggled items from your pocket

