file: /cmds/mortal/soulhist.c
keywords: mortal, emote, tellhist, shouthist, sayhist, history, communication
aliases: soulhistory
short: What did he just do from afar?
header: Command: Soulhist
::::::::::::::::::::::
    Topic: soulhist
::::::::::::::::::::::

  Syntax:  soulhist

You are in the heat of battle and among the lines of combat spam that
run across the screen, you sense that your arch nemesis has given you
a noogie from afar. But before you jump into conclusions and ask your
guild to join you in battle, you want to be sure and you can do that
by looking at the last 20 emotes that people did in your general
direction. Much to your surprise, it was your friend giving you a hug
and you feel lucky that you didn't go into a senseless circle of hate
by an optical illusion. All this thanks to 'soulhist'.


--------------------
file: /cmds/mortal/soulnew.c
keywords: mortal, soulhist, emote, reporting
aliases: 
short: What's new, what's cool and what's groovy in the realm of emotes?
header: Command: Soulnew
::::::::::::::::::::::
    Topic: soulnew
