file: /cmds/mortal/swho.c
keywords: mortal, who, finger, players, communication
aliases: 
short: Yet Another Highly Ordered List (YAHOL)
header: Topic: Swho

  Syntax: swho

You want to know who are the people who are logged on right now.
You want to know the levels of the people who are logged on right now.
You want to know all that and you would like it to be as spamless as possible.

Well, no luck here, because there will be always spam.  But, on the brighter
side, you have 'swho' that stacks all the players into four neat columns.


