file: /cmds/mortal/tagcheck.c
keywords: mortal, miscellaneous
aliases: tag, tags
short: Tag Checker
header: Topic: Tag Checker

  SYNTAX:  tagcheck

Tagcheck allows you to see which tags you currently have.
A 'tag' is utilized by a few rare monsters to indicate that you
actually fought (and likely killed) them, and prevents you from
certain actions (perhaps wearing equipment that they dropped) if
you do not have the 'tag'.

If you feel that something utilizes the 'tag' system and doesn't
appear with tagcheck, please let a wizard know.


