file: /cmds/mortal/take.c
keywords: mortal, basic, get, drop, keep, unkeep
aliases: 
short: Picking objects off the ground
header: Topic: Take

  Syntax: take <object> or take all

The lives of the rich and famous.  To be one of them is a dream
for most of us but reality for only a few.  But following this
three step program you too can be one!

   1. Kill a big monster and get a new best kill.
   2. Take the items and sell them to cancer.
   3. Buy a villa in the south of france and have many models
      walk in slim clothings around the pool.

'take all' will try to pick up everything in the room (just like
a man). The only catch in all of this is that players are human
and humans have limited strength and therefore there is an upper
limit on how much you can carry (depending on the weight of the
object you try to pick up.


