aliases: hmbolt
short: Bolt in one direction
header: Bolt

Syntax: hmbolt <valid direction>

The 'hmbolt' highmortal command will take an input of north, south,
east, west, northwest, northeast, southwest, or southeast, you will
be able to speed along up to twenty-five rooms in the specified
direction, provided there are no obstacles.
This ability costs 25 sp.  If you don't have 25sp, it costs 25 hp.

Note:  The ability to hmbolt is available at the rank of Seeker.


