--------------------
file: /cmds/himort/hmheal.c
keywords: highmortal, hm
aliases:
short: Highmortal Healing
header: hmheal

Syntax: hmheal [player/'check']

The 'hmheal' highmortal command will allow you to heal yourself or
another player.  Use the command wisely, however, for you will only
get to use each command one time per reset.
If you use the 'check' argument it will tell you when you can next
use the power.

Note: The ability to heal oneself can be used by any High Mortal.
      The ability to heal others can be used by Crusaders.
      The ability to heal others from afar can be used by Inquisitors.


