aliases: 
short: Uncursing an item
header: Hmuncurse

Syntax: hmuncurse <item>

The 'hmuncurse' highmortal command will allow you to uncurse 
a single cursed item in your inventory.

Note:  This command can only be used once/boot.
Note:  This command is available at the rank of Legend.


